<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.6.7">
<l>vallic ciṟunuṇ ṇiṭaiyā riṭainīr vaikkiṉṟa</l>
<l>allal cintai tavira vaṭaimi ṉaṭiyīrkāḷ</l>
<l>collil tiruvē yaṉaiyār kaṉivā yeyiṟoppāṉ</l>
<l>kollai mullai mellarum pīṉuṅ kuṟuṅkuṭiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Servants, to avoid distressful thoughts which you are keeping</l>
<l>Because of small, creeper-thin waisted maids, take refuge</l>
<l>In Kuṟuṅkuṭi, where clearings yield soft jasmine buds,</l>
<l>To be like teeth at the fruit[-like] lips of those who are just like Tiru in speech.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
